The '''Javreh''' are slave-soldiers of the [[Scarlet Spires]], famed for their ferocity in battle. The first unit was created in 3801 by Grandmaster [[Shinurta]] at the height of the [[Scholastic Wars]].{{EG|Javreh}}
==Members of the Javreh== * [[Geshrunni]] * [[Mamaradda]] * [[Shalmessa]] * [[Sinerses]]
