The '''Battle of Procorus''' was a decisive battle fought in 4106 between the [[Galeoth]] host under [[Coithus Saubon]] and the Imperial Army of the [[Nansur Empire|Nansur]] under [[Ikurei Conphas]] as part of the [[Galeoth Wars]]. The Galeoth host was defeated and Saubon was humiliated by Conphas.<ref>Encyclopedic Glossary, ‘Galeoth Wars’</ref><ref>''The Darkness That Comes Before,'' Chapter 17</ref>
