'''Apperens Saccarees''' is the Grandmaster of the School of [[Mandate]] at the time of the [[Great Ordeal]]. Aside from [[Anasûrimbor Kellhus]] and his daughter [[Anasûrimbor Serwa|Serwa]], only he is rumoured to have successfully recited a metagnostic cant.{{5|2}}

During the Great Ordeal as the Exalt-Magus, Saccarees is the first to see the [[Inchoroi]] rising above [[Urokkas|Mantigol]]. He laments that he should signal Kellhus as they had discussed this as their greatest peril.{{6|13}}

