The '''Battle of Kathol Pass''' was a clash between the [[Meöri Empire|Meori]] and the [[Nonmen]] of [[Cil-Aujas]] in late autumn of 2151, at the height of the [[Apocalypse]], in which the Nonman host was all but destroyed. It was known as "one of man's only victories in those dark days."{{Confirm}}

[[Category:War]]
[[Category:First Apocalypse]]

The '''Battle of Ossirish''' was a battle between [[Kûniüri]] and the [[Consult]] in 2137, during the [[Apocalypse]], in which the Consult host was routed and [[Anasûrimbor Nau-Cayûti]] killed [[Tanhafut |Tanhafut the Red]], a powerful [[Wracu]], at the height of the killing, and his corpse covered the battlefield, and the Consult fled before the victorious. Nau-Cayûti earned the name Murswagga, or 'Dragonslayer', for this feat.{{EG|Apocalypse}}
